item.name: Bytes Read Into Memcached
item.description: The number of bytes that have been read from the network by the cache node

item.name: Bytes Used For Cache Items
item.description: The number of bytes used to store cache items.

item.name: Bytes Used For Hash
item.description: The number of bytes currently used by hash tables.

item.name: Bytes Written Out From Memcached
item.description: The number of bytes that have been written to the network by the cache node.

item.name: Cas Bad val
item.description: The number of CaS (check and set) requests the cache has received where the CaS value did not match the CaS value stored.

item.name: Cas Hits
item.description: The number of Cas requests the cache has received where the requested key was found and the Cas value matched.

item.name: Cas Misses
item.description: The number of Cas requests the cache has received where the key requested was not found.

item.name: Cmd Config Get
item.description: The cumulative number of config get requests

item.name: Cmd Config Set
item.description: The cumulative number of config set requests

item.name: Cmd Flush
item.description: The number of flush commands the cache has received.

item.name: Cmd Get
item.description: The number of get commands the cache has received.

item.name: Cmd Set
item.description: The number of set commands the cache has received.

item.name: Cmd Touch
item.description: The cumulative number of touch requests.

item.name: Curr Config
item.description: The current number of configurations stored.

item.name: CurrConnections
item.description: A count of the number of connections connected to the cache at an instant in time.

item.name: CurrItems
item.description: A count of the number of items currently stored in the cache.

item.name: Decr Hits
item.description: The number of decrement requests the cache has received where the requested key was found.

item.name: Decr Misses
item.description: The number of decrement requests the cache has received where the requested key was not found.

item.name: Delete Hits
item.description: The number of delete requests the cache has received where the requested key was found.

item.name: Delete Misses
item.description: The number of delete requests the cache has received where the requested key was not found.

item.name: Evicted Unfetched
item.description: The number of valid items evicted from the least recently used cache (LRU) which were never touched after being set.

item.name: Evictions
item.description: The number of non-expired items the cache evicted to allow space for new writes.

item.name: Expired Unfetched
item.description: The number of expired items reclaimed from the LRU which were never touched after being set.

item.name: Get Hits
item.description: The number of get requests the cache has received where the key requested was found.

item.name: Get Misses
item.description: The number of get requests the cache has received where the key requested was not found.

item.name: Incr Hits
item.description: The number of increment requests the cache has received where the key requested was found.

item.name: Incr Misses
item.description: The number of increment requests the cache has received where the key requested was not found.

item.name: New Connections
item.description: The number of new connections the cache has received. This is derived from the memcached total_connections statistic by recording the change in total_connections across a period of time. This will always be at least 1, due to a connection reserved for a ElastiCache.

item.name: New Items
item.description: The number of new items the cache has stored. This is derived from the memcached total_items statistic by recording the change in total_items across a period of time.

item.name: Reclaimed
item.description: The number of expired items the cache evicted to allow space for new writes.

item.name: Slabs Moved
item.description: The total number of slab pages that have been moved.

item.name: Touch Hits
item.description: The number of keys that have been touched and were given a new expiration time.

item.name: Touch Misses
item.description: The number of items that have been touched, but were not found.

item.name: Unused Memory
item.description: The amount of unused memory the cache can use to store items. This is derived from the memcached statistics limit_maxbytes and bytes by subtracting bytes from limit_maxbytes.
